    "Alpha multiplier applied to textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Lets you fade the texture for ghost / holographic looks.": "Multiplicador alfa aplicado a caras texturizadas. 1 = opaco, 0 = invisible. Te permite desvanecer la textura para un aspecto fantasma u holográfico.",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque (wireframe hidden); 0 = invisible (wireframe only); in between = both visible.": "Multiplicador alfa aplicado a las caras texturizadas. 1 = opaco (estructura metálica oculta); 0 = invisible (solo alambre); en between = ambos visibles.",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Useful for ghost / holographic looks.": "Multiplicador alfa aplicado a las caras texturizadas. 1 = opaco, 0 = invisible. Útil para looks fantasma o holográficos.",
