    "(start)": "（開始）",
    "(unnamed)": "（未具名）",
    "+ Add Element": "+ 新增元素",
    "+ Add Plugin": "+ 新增外掛",
    "+1 = right-facing / clockwise (卐), -1 = left-facing / counter-clockwise (卍), 0 = no bends.": "+1 = 右轉/順時針（卐），-1 = 左轉/逆時針（卍），0 = 無彎曲。",
    "-- Select Command --": "-- 選擇指令 --",
    "-- Select Plugin --": "-- 選擇外掛 --",
    "0 = all drops land at the centre (clean concentric rings expanding outward). 1 = drops scattered across the full disc (chaotic raindrop pattern). Changing this recomputes the simulation.": "0 = 所有水滴落在中心（乾淨的同心環向外擴展）。1 = 散布於整個圓盤的水滴（混沌雨滴圖案）。改變這個設定會重新計算模擬。",
    "0 = parallel cylinder beam; 1 = wide cone (tip is 3× source width).": "0 = 平行圓柱樑;1 = 寬錐體（尖端為3×源寬度）。",
    "0 = ring layout (nodes on a circle), 1 = grid layout (rectangular mesh).": "0 = 環狀佈局（節點在圓形上），1 = 格狀佈局（矩形網格）。",
    "0 = sine-loop (fills then drains seamlessly); 1 = monotonic (0→100% then snaps back at the loop boundary).": "0 = 正弦迴路（充滿後無縫排水）;1 = 單調（0→100%後在環邊界反彈回來）。",
    "1 = show 45°/135° diagonal cross lines; 0 = cardinal-only.": "1 = 顯示45°/135°斜線橫線;0 = 僅基數。",
    "1 Step Backward": "退後一步",
    "10 - Maximum": "10 - 最高",
    "12-faced regular polyhedron (20 vertices, 30 edges). Golden-ratio geometry.": "12面正多面體（20個頂點，30條邊）。黃金比率幾何。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "在視圖平面上的二維旋轉（每個迴圈整圈旋轉）。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "在視圖平面上的二維旋轉（每個迴圈整圈旋轉）。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane.": "視平面上的二維旋轉。",
    "3 - Standard / Smaller": "3 - 標準/較小",
    "3D Rotation": "三維旋轉",
    "3D Rotation Control:": "3D 旋轉控制：",
    "3D arrow — shaft, pointed arrowhead, and four-vane fletching. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D箭頭——箭桿、尖頭箭頭及四葉羽翼。完整的3D旋轉+貼圖。",
    "3D bullet — true cylindrical body (14-sided lathe) capped with a curved ogive nose. Brass/copper colour by default. Full 3D rotation, lighting, and texturing.": "3D 子彈 — 真正的圓柱形彈頭（14 邊形車床），頂部為彎曲的尖頭。預設是黃銅/銅色。完整的3D旋轉、光影和貼圖。",
    "3D hammer — chunky head + long handle. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D錘頭 — 粗頭+長柄。完整的3D旋轉+貼圖。",
    "3D knife — tapered blade and grip handle. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D刀——刀刃和握把逐漸收窄。完整的3D旋轉+貼圖。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "繞 Y（垂直）軸旋轉的三維（每個迴圈旋轉數）。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "繞 Y（垂直）軸旋轉的三維（每個迴圈旋轉數）。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis.": "繞Y軸旋轉的3D。",
    "3D sword with tapered blade, crossguard, handle, and octahedral pommel. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D劍，帶有錐形刀刃、護手、劍柄及八面體劍柄。完整的3D旋轉+貼圖。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "三維繞 X 軸滾動（每個迴圈整圈旋轉）。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "三維繞 X 軸滾動（每個迴圈整圈旋轉）。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis.": "繞 X 軸進行 3D 旋轉。",
    "4D 3-sphere — nested 2-sphere cross-sections at constant w. 4D rotations mix w with x/y/z so the shells \"morph\" through each other.": "四維三維球面——巢狀的二維球面截面，w為恆定。四維旋轉將w與x/y/z混合，使殼層相互「變形」。",
    "4D 5-cell — the simplest 4-polytope, all-triangular faces. The 4D analog of a tetrahedron, rotating through extra dimensions.": "4D 5-胞體 — 最簡單的四維多胞體、全三角形面。四維版的四面體，在額外維度中旋轉。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic \"fold through w\" motion. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless.": "XW 平面上的 4D 旋轉——標誌性的「折疊穿過 w 面」動作。整數循環保持迴圈無縫。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic hypersphere \"inside-out\" inversion. Integer cycles for seamless loop.": "XW平面的四維旋轉——標誌性的超球面「內翻」反轉。整數循環以實現無縫循環。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic tesseract \"fold through w\" motion. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless. To slow it, raise the Frames count.": "XW平面上的四維旋轉——標誌性的四維立方體「折疊穿過W」運動。整數循環保持迴圈無縫。要減緩速度，可以提高幀數。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane — a second 4D fold axis. Combine with Fold A for the classic tumble. Integer cycles for seamless loop.": "ZW平面上的四維旋轉——第二個四維摺疊軸。搭配 Fold A 組合，打造經典翻滾動作。整數循環以實現無縫循環。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane — a second 4D fold axis. Combine with Fold A for the classic tumble. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless.": "ZW平面上的四維旋轉——第二個四維摺疊軸。搭配 Fold A 組合，打造經典翻滾動作。整數循環保持迴圈無縫。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane.": "ZW平面上的四維旋轉。",
    "4D tesseract wireframe rotating through extra dimensions.": "4D四維超立方體線框在額外維度中旋轉。",
