    "A black-hole / gravity-well effect: event horizon, rotating accretion disk, Einstein-ring halo, polar-distorted gravity waves, and matter spiraling inward toward the singularity.": "黑洞/重力井效應：事件視界、旋轉吸積盤、愛因斯坦環暈、極地扭曲的重力波，以及物質向奇點螺旋狀擴散。",
