    "Alpha multiplier applied to textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Lets you fade the texture for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 倍率應用於有紋理的面。1 = 不透明，0 = 隱形。可以讓你淡化紋理，做出幽靈或全息效果。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque (wireframe hidden); 0 = invisible (wireframe only); in between = both visible.": "Alpha 倍率套用在貼圖面上。1 = 不透明（線框隱藏）;0 = 隱形（僅線框）;中間 = 兩者皆可見。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Useful for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 倍率套用在貼圖面上。1 = 不透明，0 = 隱形。對鬼魂/全息影像很有用。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured surface. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Useful for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 乘法加在紋理表面。1 = 不透明，0 = 隱形。對鬼魂/全息影像很有用。",
