    "Analog-TV snow / dead-channel noise. Configurable grain size, change speed, contrast, optional color tint, CRT scanlines, and border. Drop it over an LCARS or any panel for \"system offline\" / glitch effects.": "類比電視的雪/死頻道雜訊。可調整顆粒大小、變化速度、對比度、可選色彩調色、CRT掃描線與邊框。把它放在 LCARS 或任何面板上，可以觸發「系統離線」或故障效果。",
