    "Ancient solar/auspicious symbol (Hindu, Buddhist, Jain, Norse, Native American). Defaults to the Eastern upright orientation. Use bendDirection to flip between right-facing (卐) and left-facing (卍).": "古老的太陽/吉祥象徵（印度教、佛教、耆那教、北歐、美洲原住民）。預設為東方直立姿勢。使用 bendDirection 在右向（卐）和左向（卍）之間切換。",
    "Anger": "憤怒",
    "Angle (degrees below horizontal) of the two lower diagonals. 45° is the classic.": "兩條較低對角線的角度（低於水平的度數）。45°是經典。",
    "Angular extent of each wisp as a fraction of its great circle. 0.5 = each wisp covers half a circumference; 1.0 = full ring.": "每條光線作為其大圓的分數的角度範圍。0.5 = 每根煙絲覆蓋半周;1.0 = 完整環。",
    "Angular spread of the comet tail (±half the spread is added to the trail direction). 0.15 = tight pencil trail; 1.0 = full 180° fan.": "彗星尾巴的角度擴散（±一半的擴散加到軌跡方向上）。0.15 = 緊湊的鉛筆軌跡;1.0 = 全風扇180°。",
    "Angular width of each blade. 60° = classic trefoil with equal gaps.": "每片刀片的角度寬度。60° = 經典三葉形且間隙相等。",
    "Angular width of each ray as a fraction of its slot (1 = rays touch, 0 = invisible).": "每條射線的角寬度為其槽位的分數（1 = 射線接觸，0 = 不可見）。",
    "Angular width of the rotating sweep wedge. 20° = thin laser, 90° = quarter-disc wash.": "旋轉掃楔的角寬度。20° = 薄雷射，90° = 四分之一圓盤洗滌。",
