    "Kaleidoscopic psychedelic mandala — N-fold mirror-symmetric radial pattern with overlapping sinusoidal noise and HSL colour cycling. Crank Symmetry, Flow Speed, and Color Speed for maximum trip.": "萬花筒迷幻曼荼羅——N重鏡對稱放射狀圖案，帶有重疊的正弦波噪聲與HSL色彩循環。曲柄對稱、流量和色彩速度，以達到最大行程。",
    "Karplus-Strong string dampening. Higher = longer ringing decay. Only affects Karplus waveform.": "Karplus-Strong 弦阻尼。較高 = 更長的響鈴衰減。只影響 Karplus 波形。",
