    "Number of bands from the centre to the rim. Higher = finer bands.": "從中心到邊緣的帶狀數量。較高 = 帶狀物較細。",
    "Number of bars in the bar graph. 1 = single column, 24 = dense histogram.": "柱狀圖中的柱數。1 = 單欄，24 = 密集直方圖。",
    "Number of blades around the center. 3 = classic trefoil.": "中間有幾片刀片。3 = 經典三葉形。",
    "Number of blinking indicator dots in the bottom status bar.": "底部狀態列中閃爍的指示點數量。",
    "Number of bright highlight sparks scattered around the ring. 0 = no sparks.": "擂台上散落著許多明亮的高光火花。0 = 無火花。",
    "Number of bright sparkles WITHIN each flame tongue (riding along the centerline). 0 = no internal sizzle.": "每個火焰舌內（沿著中心線排列）中閃爍的亮粉數量。0 = 無內部滋滋聲。",
    "Number of byte-columns per row. 4 = wide bytes, 32 = dense.": "每列的位元組欄數。4 = 寬位元組，32 = 密集位元組。",
    "Number of byte-rows in the dump. 4 = sparse, 24 = packed.": "傾倒中的位元組列數。4 = 稀疏，24 = 填充。",
    "Number of coloured segments inside the top and bottom horizontal bars.": "上下水平條內的彩色段數。",
    "Number of concentric range rings.": "同心圓環的數量。",
    "Number of contact blips on the radar.": "雷達上的接觸點數量。",
    "Number of curl waves along each wisp.": "每條光線上的捲曲波數量。",
    "Number of drop points emitting ripples.": "釋放漣漪的投放點數量。",
    "Number of droplets that eject from each drop on impact. 0 disables.": "每滴落地中噴出的水滴數量。0 失能。",
    "Number of drops scheduled evenly across the loop. Each drop kicks the water and sustains the ripple field. More drops = more agitated surface / more rings. Changing this recomputes the simulation.": "整個環路平均排定的投放數量。每一滴水都踢動水面並維持波紋場。更多的滴落 = 攪動的表面更多 / 更多的環。改變這個設定會重新計算模擬。",
    "Number of ember sparks rising ABOVE the flame. 0 = no embers.": "火焰上方升起的火星數量。0 = 無火星。",
    "Number of flame tongues. More = denser flame with more overlapping tongues.": "火焰舌頭的數量。More = 火焰密度較高，且舌頭重疊更多。",
    "Number of floating pill buttons in the top-right area of the central display.": "中央螢幕右上角浮動的藥丸按鈕數量。",
    "Number of full rotations from bottom to top of the helix.": "從螺旋底部到頂部的完整旋轉次數。",
    "Number of great-circle wisp arcs distributed across the sphere surface. More = denser energy weave covering the bubble.": "分布於球面上的大圓光弧數量。更多 = 覆蓋氣泡的能量密度較高。",
    "Number of grid cells across each axis.": "每個軸上的格網格數量。",
    "Number of horizontal rings stacked along the column.": "柱子上堆疊的水平環數量。",
    "Number of horizontal scanlines across the panel.": "面板上水平掃描線的數量。",
    "Number of light pulses traveling along each edge simultaneously. 0 = static network.": "同時沿著每條邊傳播的光脈衝數量。0 = 靜態網路。",
    "Number of lightning arcs travelling around the surface. 0 = no arcs.": "在地表上移動的閃電弧線數量。0 = 無弧線。",
    "Number of matter streaks spiraling inward toward the horizon. 0 disables.": "有多少條物質條紋螺旋向地平線延伸。0 失能。",
    "Number of monitor rows. 1 = single vital; 8 = dense panel.": "螢幕列數。1 = 單一生命徵象;8 = 密集面板。",
    "Number of moving unit icons on the map.": "地圖上移動單位圖示的數量。",
    "Number of nodes in the network.": "網路中的節點數量。",
    "Number of particles drifting through the cylinder.": "通過圓柱體漂移的粒子數量。",
    "Number of pseudo-text rows in the central display.": "中央顯示的偽文字列數。",
    "Number of pseudo-text rows in the data area. 0 = no text rows.": "資料區中偽文字列數。0 = 無文字列。",
    "Number of radial scan lines rotating inside the inner ring. 0 = none.": "內環內旋轉的放射狀掃描線數量。0 = 無。",
    "Number of ray-planes rotated around the vertical axis. 1 = flat 2D fan (legacy look); 3+ = true spherical starburst with rays radiating in 3D in all directions. Higher = more solid 3D ball but more rendering cost.": "繞垂直軸旋轉的射線平面數量。1 = 平面二維風扇（舊有風格）;3+ = 真正的球形星爆，射線向所有方向輻射三維。越高 = 3D 球體越堅固，但渲染成本越高。",
    "Number of rays radiating from the center.": "從中心輻射出的射線數量。",
    "Number of ribbon petals per tongue, rotated around the tongue's vertical axis. 1 = flat sheet (legacy 2D look); 3-4 = true volumetric flame finger that reads as 3D from any angle. Higher = more solid look but more rendering cost.": "每個舌頭的緞帶花瓣數，繞著舌頭的垂直軸旋轉。1 = 平面板（傳統二維外觀）;3-4 = 從任何角度讀取為三維的真實體積火焰指。越高 = 外觀越穩定，但渲染成本越高。",
    "Number of sine ripples along beam length. 0 = perfectly straight.": "沿著光束長度的正弦波紋數量。0 = 完全直線。",
    "Number of sine waves along each wisp.": "每條光線上的正弦波數量。",
    "Number of tendrils emanating from the centre.": "從中心伸出的觸鬚數量。",
    "Number of vertical pill buttons stacked along the left spine between the elbows.": "左側脊椎肘間堆疊著許多垂直的藥丸按鈕。",
    "Number of visible log lines. 3 = sparse status; 16 = packed.": "可見的對白線數。3 = 罕見狀態;16 = 已打包。",
