    "Primary color used in top/bottom bar segments and some pills.": "主色用於上下酒吧段落和某些藥丸。",
    "Priority": "優先權",
    "Probability of optional cross-chord (ring) or distance-link (grid) edges. Ring topology always includes neighbor edges.": "可選的交叉弦（環）或距離連結（網格）邊的機率。環形拓撲總是包含鄰邊。",
    "Procedural / Outfit / Hair Forge parts are JS templates and appear on the Procedural tab, not here.": "程序化/服裝/髮型鍛造的零件是 JS 模板，顯示在程序化標籤，不是這裡。",
    "Procedural hair aligned to the active body head and eye-line anchors, with frame-aware walk bobbing.": "程序化髮型對齊於主動身體頭部與視線錨點，並具備框架感知的走路擺動。",
    "Procedural rising flame — particles rise from a base, fade hot-core to cool-tip, with adjustable turbulence and flicker.": "程序化上升火焰——粒子從基底上升，逐漸從熱芯淡出至冷頂端，並可調整湍流與閃爍。",
    "Procedural snowflake crystal with animated branching arms, ice-shimmer sparkles, and a rotating inner hexagon.": "程序化的雪花水晶，帶有動畫分支手臂、冰晶閃爍的閃爍，以及旋轉的內六角形。",
