    "Purchase Only": "僅限購買",
    "Pure sine, immediate attack, long ringing decay.": "純正弦波，立即攻擊，長時間的振鈴衰減。",
    "Q at the lowpass cutoff. Higher = sharper resonant peak (synth laser). 1 = flat rolloff.": "Q 在低通關口。較高 = 共振峰值更銳利（合成雷射）。1 = 平滑滾落。",
    "Question": "問題",
    "Quick square chirp with upward pitch.": "快速的方形啾啾聲，音調向上。",
    "RPG Reactor Web could not start: {error}": "RPG 反應爐網路無法啟動：{error}",
    "Radial explosion burst with hot core flash, expanding shockwave ring, debris particles, and smoke dissipation.": "徑向爆炸伴隨熱核心閃光、擴張的衝擊波環、碎片粒子及煙霧散散。",
    "Radial perturbation amount for the wispy curves — how much they bulge in/out from the mean radius.": "對於細微曲線的徑向擾動量——它們從平均半徑中凸出的程度。",
    "Radial rays from a glowing core with optional rotation + pulse. Holy bursts, sunbeams, lens flares, beacons.": "來自發光核心的徑向射線，並可選旋轉+脈衝。神聖的爆發、陽光、透鏡光斑、信標。",
    "Radial thickness of the ring annulus (outer − inner radius).": "環環的徑向厚度（外側−內半徑）。",
    "Radius at the narrow base/tip (fraction of half-frame). Classic tornado has this much smaller than top.": "窄底/尖端的半徑（半框比例）。經典龍捲風的這個比頂部小很多。",
    "Radius at the wide top of the funnel (fraction of half-frame). Set smaller than base for inverted/drain vortex.": "漏斗寬頂端的半徑（半框比例）。設定比底層小，適合倒置/排水渦流。",
    "Radius multiplier for the central glow disc.": "中央發光盤的半徑倍增器。",
    "Radius of the central disc (fraction of outer radius).": "中央椎間盤半徑（外半徑的比例）。",
    "Radius of the central glow as a fraction of the disc radius.": "中心光芒半徑為圓盤半徑的分數。",
    "Radius of the portal disc as a fraction of the size. Smaller = tighter portal.": "門盤半徑以大小的分數表示。小一點=更緊密的傳送門。",
    "Radius of the spherical bubble in local units. Smaller = tighter shield.": "球形氣泡的半徑（以局部單位為單位）。較小=護盾更緊密。",
    "Rage": "憤怒",
    "Rainbow-colored energy tendrils emanating from a central bright point. Each wisp is a tapered curving tendril with halo/body/core lighting. Spread, count, length, wobble, and rainbow rotation are all tunable.": "彩虹色的能量觸手從中央明亮點散發出來。每根光芒都是錐形彎曲的觸手，帶有光環/身體/核心光照。擴散、計數、長度、晃動和彩虹旋轉都是可調的。",
