    "Spherical force-field bubble around its center. Energy wisps are great-circle arcs distributed evenly across the sphere surface, with silhouette-weighted alpha so the bubble outline reads brightest at the rim (fresnel-edged). Use it as a shield/aura around a character or object.": "中心周圍有球形力場氣泡。能量光線是均勻分布在球面的大圓弧，帶有輪廓加權的阿爾法，使氣泡輪廓在邊緣（菲涅爾邊緣）最亮。用它當作護盾或光環包圍角色或物品。",
    "Spread of brightness between dark and bright pixels. 0 = flat mid-grey; 1 = full black-to-white range.": "亮度在暗與亮之間分布。0 = 平坦的中灰色;1 = 全黑到白範圍。",
