    "Star Trek-style LCARS console with the iconic curved elbows, coloured pill buttons, segmented top/bottom bars, and a central display populated with scrolling pseudo-text. Defaults to canonical LCARS palette.": "星際爭霸戰風格的LCARS主機，擁有標誌性的彎曲肘部、彩色藥丸按鈕、分段上下橫桿，以及中央顯示滾動的偽文字。預設為正統的 LCARS 調色盤。",
    "Star-Trek-transporter-style energy column: stacked glowing rings around a vertical axis, drifting particle field inside the cylinder, and optional data-fragment overlays. Tilt the column to reveal each ring as a real 3D ellipse.": "類似《星際爭霸戰》傳送器的能量柱：圍繞垂直軸層疊起發光環、圓柱體內漂浮的粒子場，以及可選的資料片段疊加。傾斜柱子，即可顯示每個環作為真實的3D橢圓。",
    "Stargate-style event horizon with deterministic rain drops driving a periodic ripple field. Per-pixel refraction warps the base radial gradient for the rippling-liquid look.": "星門式事件視界，帶有確定性的雨滴驅動週期性的漣漪場。每像素折射會扭曲基底徑向漸變，形成波紋般的液體效果。",
