    "The $ symbol — S-curve with a vertical bar through it. Full 3D rotation.": "$符號 — 帶有一條垂直橫條的S形曲線。完整的3D旋轉。",
    "The Soviet emblem — a sickle blade crossed by a hammer. Geometry ported from the canonical flag SVG. Full 3D rotation.": "蘇聯徽章——一把鐮刀刀刃交叉，上面有錘子。幾何圖形是從經典旗幟 SVG 移植而來。完整的3D旋轉。",
