    "The project metadata or map list could not be saved.": "專案的元資料或地圖清單無法儲存。",
    "The taijitu — a disc divided by an S-curve into two interlocking teardrops with opposite-colored dots in each. Full 3D rotation.": "太極圖——一個由S形曲線分成兩個互鎖淚滴，每個淚滴中有相反顏色的點。完整的3D旋轉。",
    "The ¥ symbol — Y diagonals + vertical descender + two crossbars. Full 3D rotation.": "¥符號 — Y對角線+垂直下降線+兩個橫桿。完整的3D旋轉。",
    "The € symbol — C-arc with two horizontal bars. Full 3D rotation.": "€符號 — 帶有兩條橫條的C弧。完整的3D旋轉。",
    "There are unsaved changes in": "有未儲存的變更",
