    "Vertical center of the horizontal arm. 0 = centered (Greek cross); 0.3 = upper third (Latin).": "水平手臂的垂直中心。0 = 居中（希臘十字）;0.3 = 上三分之一（拉丁文）。",
    "Vertical center of the shape (fraction of frame height). 0 = top, 0.5 = center, 1 = bottom.": "形狀的垂直中心（相對於框架高度的比例）。0 = 上方，0.5 = 中心，1 = 下方。",
    "Vertical cycles each particle completes per loop. Integer for seamless looping.": "垂直循環：每個粒子每圈完成一次。整數則是為了無縫循環。",
    "Vertical extent of the column (column height as a fraction of size). 1.0 = column-as-tall-as-wide, 1.6 = taller transporter pad.": "柱的垂直範圍（柱高以尺寸的比例計算）。1.0 = 柱高與寬相同，1.6 = 較高的運輸墊。",
    "Vertical extent of the tornado (fraction of frame height).": "龍捲風的垂直範圍（佔框架高度的比例）。",
    "Vertical extent of the waveform within its zone. 0 = flatline.": "波形在其區域內的垂直範圍。0 = 平線。",
    "Vertical extent of where drops spawn (fraction of frame height). 0 = all on a horizontal line.": "掉落生成的垂直範圍（佔幀高的比例）。0 = 所有在水平線上。",
    "Vertical position (fraction of frame height). 0 = top, 0.5 = center, 1 = bottom.": "垂直位置（佔畫面高度的比例）。0 = 上方，0.5 = 中心，1 = 下方。",
    "Vertical position of the 4-point star (USSF default: -0.28, in the lower interior). Negative = lower, positive = upper.": "四角星的垂直位置（美國足球協會預設：-0.28，位於下方內部）。負 = 較低，正 = 上。",
    "Vertical position of the flame base (0 = top of frame, 1 = bottom). Default 0.8 puts the base near the bottom edge.": "火焰底座的垂直位置（0 = 框架頂部，1 = 底部）。預設的 0.8 會把底座放在底部邊緣附近。",
    "Vertical position of the ring (above triangle apex, ≈0.81 by default).": "環的垂直位置（三角形頂點上方，≈預設為0.81）。",
    "Vertical reach of each waveform. 0.2 = flat, 1.5 = clipping into neighbor row.": "每個波形的垂直範圍。0.2 = 平坦，1.5 = 剪裁到鄰列。",
    "Vertical scale of the helix. 1 = unit cube (default), 0.3 = squat, 2-3 = tall and stretched.": "螺旋的垂直比例。1 = 單位立方體（預設），0.3 = 深蹲，2-3 = 高大且伸展。",
    "Vest 01": "背心 01",
    "Victory": "勝利",
    "Violet": "紫羅蘭",
    "Visibility of the annular ring above the apex.": "頂點上方環狀環的可見度。",
    "Visibility of the inner chevron shape. 0 = single outer triangle, no chevron.": "內部倒V形的可見度。0 = 單一外三角形，無倒V形。",
    "Visual size of each node dot.": "每個節點點的視覺大小。",
    "Visual size of each particle.": "每個粒子的視覺大小。",
    "Void Crimson": "虛空赤紅",
    "Vol:": "卷：",
    "Volume": "音量",
    "Volume wobble depth. 0 = none, 1 = amplitude oscillates fully (0 to peak). Creates \"wa-wa\" or alarm effects.": "音量晃動深度。0 = 無，1 = 振幅完全振盪（0 到 峰值）。會產生「哇哇」或警報效果。",
    "Volume wobble speed (Hz). Low = slow swell, high = motorboat / buzzer.": "音量擺動速度（Hz）。低浪 = 慢浪，高浪 = 摩托艇 / 蜂鳴器。",
