    "Warning: This will remove entries": "警告：此將移除條目",
    "Waveshaper distortion amount. For Karplus: pluck hardness (0 = mellow, 1 = bright/clicky).": "波形塑形器失真量。對 Karplus 來說：撥弦硬度（0 = 溫和，1 = 明亮/喀嗒聲）。",
    "Wavy surface chop on each ring outline. 0 = perfect circles, 1.5 = roiling sea.": "每個環輪廓上有波浪狀的切割。0 = 完美圓，1.5 = 翻滾的海。",
