    "Web (HTML5)": "網頁（HTML5）",
    "WebGL initialization failed": "WebGL 初始化失敗",
    "When": "當",
    "When Cancel": "取消時",
    "Where the rays START (distance from center, fraction of frame). 0 = rays start from the point center.": "射線開始的位置（距離中心的距離，幀的比例）。0 = 射線從點中心開始。",
    "Whip": "鞭子",
    "White-hot center of the beam.": "光束中心白熱。",
    "Whole 2D rotations in the screen plane per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每個迴圈在螢幕平面上做完整的二維旋轉。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "Whole 2D rotations in the view plane during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "動畫過程中視角平面會整個 2D 旋轉。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。",
    "Whole Map": "全地圖",
    "Whole cycles per loop of the underlying noise waves. Integer for seamless looping. Higher = more violent motion.": "每個迴路的整個週期是底層噪聲波的。整數則是為了無縫循環。越高 = 運動越劇烈。",
    "Whole hue rotations per loop. Integer keeps loop seamless. 0 = static colors.": "每個循環的全色旋轉。整數讓迴圈保持無縫。0 = 靜態顏色。",
    "Whole orbits per loop. Integer for seamless looping. 0 = stationary head — use Static Angle to point the tail.": "每圈繞圈數。整數則是為了無縫循環。0 = 靜止頭部 — 使用靜態角度指向尾部。",
    "Whole rainbow cycles per loop (hue rotation over time). Integer for seamless looping. 0 = static palette.": "每個循環都有完整的彩虹週期（色相隨時間旋轉）。整數則是為了無縫循環。0 = 靜態調色盤。",
    "Whole rotations around the X axis per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每個迴圈繞 X 軸旋轉整圈。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "Whole rotations around the Y axis per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每個迴圈繞 Y 軸旋轉整圈。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "Whole rotations around the vertical axis during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow apparent rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "動畫中繞垂直軸旋轉整個過程。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。為了減緩表面旋轉，請提高頂部的幀數。",
    "Whole rotations around the vertical axis during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "動畫中繞垂直軸旋轉整個過程。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。要減緩旋轉，請將頂端的幀數提高。",
    "Whole rotations forward/back during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow apparent rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "動畫中整個前後旋轉。整數值讓迴圈保持無縫。為了減緩表面旋轉，請提高頂部的幀數。",
    "Whole rotations of the kaleidoscope pattern per loop. Integer for seamless looping. Positive = clockwise, negative = counter-clockwise, 0 = no rotation.": "每圈萬花筒圖案的整圈旋轉。整數則是為了無縫循環。正 = 順時針，負 = 逆時針，0 = 無旋轉。",
    "Whole rotations of the ring vertices around the column axis per loop. Integer keeps the loop seamless.": "每個環繞柱軸的整個頂點旋轉。整數讓迴圈保持無縫。",
    "Whole rotations of the wisps around the ring per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每個環繞環繞繞整個光束旋轉。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "Whole rotations per loop. Positive = clockwise illusion (inward draw); negative = counter-clockwise (outward push). Integer for seamless loop.": "每圈整圈旋轉。正向 = 順時針錯覺（向內抽）;負 = 逆時針方向（向外推）。整數代表無縫迴圈。",
    "Whole shimmer-wave cycles per loop along the tail. Integer = seamless loop. 0 = wisps hold a fixed shape; higher = more flowing/rippling motion.": "整個閃爍波週期沿著尾部每個迴圈。整數 = 無縫迴圈。0 = 光束保持固定形狀;較高=流動/波紋運動更多。",
    "Whoosh slash through air.": "呼嘯斬穿空氣。",
    "Width at the source (cone base).": "源頭（錐體底座）的寬度。",
    "Width of the bright core as fraction of beam width.": "明亮核心的寬度佔光束寬度的比例。",
    "Width of the optional rectangular border around the panel. 0 = no border.": "面板周圍可選長方形邊框的寬度。0 = 無邊界。",
    "Width of the vertical bar (fraction of half-size).": "垂直條寬度（半尺寸的比例）。",
