    "+ Add Plugin": "+ 添加插件",
    "+1 = right-facing / clockwise (卐), -1 = left-facing / counter-clockwise (卍), 0 = no bends.": "+1 = 右向 / 顺时针（卐），-1 = 向左 / 逆时针（卍），0 = 无弯道。",
    "-- Select Command --": "-- 选择命令 --",
    "-- Select Plugin --": "——选择插件——",
    "0 = all drops land at the centre (clean concentric rings expanding outward). 1 = drops scattered across the full disc (chaotic raindrop pattern). Changing this recomputes the simulation.": "0 = 所有水滴落在中心（干净的同心环向外扩展）。1 = 散布在整个圆盘上的水滴（混沌雨滴模式）。改变这个条件会重新计算模拟。",
    "0 = parallel cylinder beam; 1 = wide cone (tip is 3× source width).": "0 = 平行圆柱梁;1 = 宽锥（尖端为3×源宽）。",
    "0 = ring layout (nodes on a circle), 1 = grid layout (rectangular mesh).": "0 = 环形布局（节点在圆上），1 = 网格布局（矩形网格）。",
    "0 = sine-loop (fills then drains seamlessly); 1 = monotonic (0→100% then snaps back at the loop boundary).": "0 = 正弦环（填充后无缝排水）;1 = 单调（0→100%后在环边界反弹）。",
    "1 = show 45°/135° diagonal cross lines; 0 = cardinal-only.": "1 = 显示45°/135°对角线横线;0 = 仅基数。",
    "1 Step Backward": "一步倒退",
    "10 - Maximum": "10 - 最高",
    "12-faced regular polyhedron (20 vertices, 30 edges). Golden-ratio geometry.": "12面正多面体（20个顶点，30条边）。黄金比几何。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "视平面上的二维旋转（每个环圈的整旋转数）。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "视平面上的二维旋转（每个环圈的整旋转数）。整数值保持循环无缝。",
    "2D rotation in the view plane.": "视野平面上的二维旋转。",
    "3 - Standard / Smaller": "3 - 标准 / 小",
    "3D Rotation": "三维旋转",
    "3D Rotation Control:": "3D旋转控制：",
    "3D arrow — shaft, pointed arrowhead, and four-vane fletching. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D箭——箭杆、尖头箭头和四叶箭羽。全3D旋转+贴图。",
    "3D bullet — true cylindrical body (14-sided lathe) capped with a curved ogive nose. Brass/copper colour by default. Full 3D rotation, lighting, and texturing.": "3D子弹——真正的圆柱形弹头（14边形车床），顶部为弧形尖头。默认是黄铜/铜色。完整的3D旋转、光照和贴图。",
    "3D hammer — chunky head + long handle. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D锤子——粗头+长柄。全3D旋转+贴图。",
    "3D knife — tapered blade and grip handle. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "3D刀具——锥形刀刃和握把。全3D旋转+贴图。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "绕Y轴（垂直轴）进行三维旋转（每圈旋转数）。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "绕Y轴（垂直轴）进行三维旋转（每圈旋转数）。整数值保持循环无缝。",
    "3D spin around the Y (vertical) axis.": "绕Y轴（垂直轴）进行三维旋转。",
    "3D sword with tapered blade, crossguard, handle, and octahedral pommel. Full 3D rotation + texturing.": "带有锥形刀刃、横护手、手柄和八面体剑柄的立体剑。全3D旋转+贴图。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "绕X轴的三维旋转（每圈整圈旋转）。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "绕X轴的三维旋转（每圈整圈旋转）。整数值保持循环无缝。",
    "3D tumble around the X axis.": "绕X轴进行三维旋转。",
    "4D 3-sphere — nested 2-sphere cross-sections at constant w. 4D rotations mix w with x/y/z so the shells \"morph\" through each other.": "四维三维球面——嵌套的二维球面截面，w值恒定。四维旋转将w与x/y/z混合，使壳层相互“变形”。",
    "4D 5-cell — the simplest 4-polytope, all-triangular faces. The 4D analog of a tetrahedron, rotating through extra dimensions.": "4D 5-胞体——最简单的4维多胞体，全三角形面。四维版的四面体，在额外维度中旋转。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic \"fold through w\" motion. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless.": "XW平面上的4D旋转——标志性的“折穿W”运动。整数循环保持循环无缝。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic hypersphere \"inside-out\" inversion. Integer cycles for seamless loop.": "XW平面的四维旋转——标志性的超球“反转”。整数循环实现无缝循环。",
    "4D rotation in the XW plane — the iconic tesseract \"fold through w\" motion. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless. To slow it, raise the Frames count.": "XW平面上的四维旋转——标志性的四维立方体“折叠穿过W”运动。整数循环保持循环无缝。要减缓速度，提高帧数。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane — a second 4D fold axis. Combine with Fold A for the classic tumble. Integer cycles for seamless loop.": "ZW平面上的四维旋转——第二个四维折叠轴。与Fold A结合，经典翻滚动作。整数循环实现无缝循环。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane — a second 4D fold axis. Combine with Fold A for the classic tumble. Integer cycles keep the loop seamless.": "ZW平面上的四维旋转——第二个四维折叠轴。与Fold A结合，经典翻滚动作。整数循环保持循环无缝。",
    "4D rotation in the ZW plane.": "零波平面上的四维旋转。",
    "4D tesseract wireframe rotating through extra dimensions.": "四维四维超立方体线框在额外维度中旋转。",
