    "A black-hole / gravity-well effect: event horizon, rotating accretion disk, Einstein-ring halo, polar-distorted gravity waves, and matter spiraling inward toward the singularity.": "黑洞/引力井效应：事件视界、旋转吸积盘、爱因斯坦环晕、极地扭曲的引力波，以及物质向奇点螺旋式扩散。",
