    "Alpha multiplier applied to textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Lets you fade the texture for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 乘数应用在纹理面上。1 = 不透明，0 = 隐形。这样可以淡化纹理，做出幽灵/全息效果。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque (wireframe hidden); 0 = invisible (wireframe only); in between = both visible.": "Alpha 乘数应用到纹理面上。1 = 不透明（线框隐藏）;0 = 不可见（仅线框）;中间 = 两者都可见。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured faces. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Useful for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 乘数应用到纹理面上。1 = 不透明，0 = 隐形。对幽灵/全息视觉效果很有用。",
    "Alpha multiplier applied to the textured surface. 1 = opaque, 0 = invisible. Useful for ghost / holographic looks.": "Alpha 乘法器应用到纹理表面。1 = 不透明，0 = 隐形。对幽灵/全息视觉效果很有用。",
    "Also create Linux AppImage": "还要创建 Linux AppImage",
    "Always Dash": "永远冲刺",
    "Analog-TV snow / dead-channel noise. Configurable grain size, change speed, contrast, optional color tint, CRT scanlines, and border. Drop it over an LCARS or any panel for \"system offline\" / glitch effects.": "模拟电视的雪/死频道噪声。可配置颗粒大小、变速、对比度、可选色彩色调、CRT扫描线和边框。把它放在LCARS或其他面板上，做“系统离线”/故障效果。",
