    "Analyzing {file}...": "分析{file}......",
    "Ancient solar/auspicious symbol (Hindu, Buddhist, Jain, Norse, Native American). Defaults to the Eastern upright orientation. Use bendDirection to flip between right-facing (卐) and left-facing (卍).": "古老的太阳/吉祥符号（印度教、佛教、耆那教、北欧、美洲原住民）。默认为东方直立朝向。使用bendDirection在右向（卐）和左向（卍）之间切换。",
    "Anger": "愤怒",
    "Angle (degrees below horizontal) of the two lower diagonals. 45° is the classic.": "两个下斜线的角度（低于水平的度数）。45°是经典。",
    "Angular extent of each wisp as a fraction of its great circle. 0.5 = each wisp covers half a circumference; 1.0 = full ring.": "每根细丝的角范围，作为其大圆的分数。0.5 = 每根丝线覆盖半周;1.0 = 全环。",
    "Angular spread of the comet tail (±half the spread is added to the trail direction). 0.15 = tight pencil trail; 1.0 = full 180° fan.": "彗星尾巴的角扩散（±扩散的一半加到尾迹方向）。0.15 = 铅笔尾距紧;1.0 = 满180°风扇。",
    "Angular width of each blade. 60° = classic trefoil with equal gaps.": "每片刀刃的角宽。60° = 经典三叶形且间隙相等。",
    "Angular width of each ray as a fraction of its slot (1 = rays touch, 0 = invisible).": "每条射线的角宽度为其缝隙的分数（1 = 接触射线，0 = 不可见）。",
    "Angular width of the rotating sweep wedge. 20° = thin laser, 90° = quarter-disc wash.": "旋转扫楔的角宽。20° = 薄激光，90° = 四分之一盘洗。",
