    "Animated targeting reticle. Brackets snap inward to acquire the target, then pulse when locked. Optional rotating scan lines + jittery center.": "动画瞄准准星。支架内扣以锁定目标，锁定时脉冲。可选旋转扫描线+抖动中心。",
