    "Kaleidoscopic psychedelic mandala — N-fold mirror-symmetric radial pattern with overlapping sinusoidal noise and HSL colour cycling. Crank Symmetry, Flow Speed, and Color Speed for maximum trip.": "万花筒迷幻曼荼罗——N重镜对称径向图案，带有重叠的正弦噪声和HSL色彩循环。曲柄对称性、流速和色彩速度，以实现最大行程。",
