    "Number of bands from the centre to the rim. Higher = finer bands.": "从中心到边缘的条带数量。越高=条纹越细。",
    "Number of bars in the bar graph. 1 = single column, 24 = dense histogram.": "柱状图中的柱数。1 = 单列，24 = 密集直方图。",
    "Number of blades around the center. 3 = classic trefoil.": "中心周围有多少刀片。3 = 经典三叶形。",
    "Number of blinking indicator dots in the bottom status bar.": "底部状态栏中闪烁的指示点数量。",
    "Number of bright highlight sparks scattered around the ring. 0 = no sparks.": "场上散布着许多明亮的高光火花。0 = 无火花。",
    "Number of bright sparkles WITHIN each flame tongue (riding along the centerline). 0 = no internal sizzle.": "每个火焰舌内（沿中心线排列）的亮光数量。0 = 无内部滋滋声。",
    "Number of byte-columns per row. 4 = wide bytes, 32 = dense.": "每行字节列数。4 = 宽字节，32 = 稠密字节。",
    "Number of byte-rows in the dump. 4 = sparse, 24 = packed.": "倾倒中的字节行数。4 = 稀疏，24 = 填充。",
    "Number of coloured segments inside the top and bottom horizontal bars.": "上下横条内的彩色段数。",
    "Number of concentric range rings.": "同心圆环的数量。",
    "Number of contact blips on the radar.": "雷达上的接触点数。",
    "Number of curl waves along each wisp.": "每丝线上卷曲波的数量。",
    "Number of drop points emitting ripples.": "释放涟漪的投放点数量。",
    "Number of droplets that eject from each drop on impact. 0 disables.": "每滴落地喷射的水滴数量。0 禁用。",
    "Number of drops scheduled evenly across the loop. Each drop kicks the water and sustains the ripple field. More drops = more agitated surface / more rings. Changing this recomputes the simulation.": "整个环路平均安排的投放数量。每一滴水都踢动水面，维持波纹场。更多的滴落=更多的搅拌表面/更多的环。改变这个条件会重新计算模拟。",
    "Number of ember sparks rising ABOVE the flame. 0 = no embers.": "火焰上方升起的火星数量。0 = 无火星。",
    "Number of flame tongues. More = denser flame with more overlapping tongues.": "火焰舌的数量。More = 火焰密度更高，舌头重叠更多。",
    "Number of floating pill buttons in the top-right area of the central display.": "中央显示屏右上角浮动的药丸按钮数量。",
    "Number of full rotations from bottom to top of the helix.": "从螺旋底部到顶部的全旋转次数。",
    "Number of great-circle wisp arcs distributed across the sphere surface. More = denser energy weave covering the bubble.": "分布在球面上的大圆光弧数量。更多=覆盖气泡的能量织物密度更高。",
    "Number of grid cells across each axis.": "每个轴上的网格单元数量。",
    "Number of horizontal rings stacked along the column.": "柱子上堆叠的水平环数量。",
