    "Number of radial scan lines rotating inside the inner ring. 0 = none.": "内环内旋转的径向扫描线数量。0 = 无。",
    "Number of ray-planes rotated around the vertical axis. 1 = flat 2D fan (legacy look); 3+ = true spherical starburst with rays radiating in 3D in all directions. Higher = more solid 3D ball but more rendering cost.": "绕垂直轴旋转的射线平面数量。1 = 平面二维风扇（传统风格）;3+ = 真正的球形星爆，射线向所有方向辐射三维。越高=3D球体更坚固，但渲染成本越高。",
    "Number of rays radiating from the center.": "从中心辐射出的射线数量。",
