    "STATIC 3D tilt around the X axis (degrees) applied after 4D perspective. Use the gizmo to set the viewing angle.": "在4D透视后，围绕X轴（度数）进行静态3D倾斜。用这个装置来设置视角。",
    "STATIC 3D tilt around the X axis (degrees) applied after 4D perspective. Use the rotation gizmo to set the viewing angle.": "在4D透视后，围绕X轴（度数）进行静态3D倾斜。用旋转装置来设置视角。",
