    "STATIC tilt around the X axis (degrees). 23° matches Earth's axial tilt. Applied before rotation.": "围绕X轴（度数）的静态倾斜。23°与地球的轴倾角相符。在旋转前涂抹。",
    "STATIC tilt around the X axis (degrees). Applied before rotation cycles. Use to set the initial orientation of the shape.": "围绕X轴（度数）的静态倾斜。在轮换周期前施用。用来设置形状的初始方向。",
    "STATIC tilt around the X axis (degrees). Tumbles the symbol forward/back.": "围绕X轴（度数）的静态倾斜。符号前后滚动。",
    "STATIC tilt around the Y axis (degrees). Changes where the texture's \"front\" faces.": "静电倾斜绕Y轴（度数）。改变纹理“正面”的方向。",
    "STATIC tilt around the Y axis (degrees). Spins the symbol like a coin face-on/face-away.": "静电倾斜绕Y轴（度数）。像硬币一样旋转符号，正面或背面。",
    "STATIC tilt around the Y axis (degrees). Use to face a different side of the shape forward.": "静电倾斜绕Y轴（度数）。用来面向形状的另一侧。",
