    "Star Trek-style LCARS console with the iconic curved elbows, coloured pill buttons, segmented top/bottom bars, and a central display populated with scrolling pseudo-text. Defaults to canonical LCARS palette.": "星际迷航风格的LCARS控制台，标志性的弯曲肘部、彩色药丸按钮、分段上下栏，以及中央显示滚动的伪文本。默认使用正规的LCARS调色板。",
    "Star-Trek-transporter-style energy column: stacked glowing rings around a vertical axis, drifting particle field inside the cylinder, and optional data-fragment overlays. Tilt the column to reveal each ring as a real 3D ellipse.": "类似《星际迷航》传送器的能量柱：围绕垂直轴层叠放发光环，圆柱体内漂浮粒子场，以及可选的数据碎片叠加层。倾斜柱子，就能看到每个环作为真实的三维椭圆。",
    "Stargate-style event horizon with deterministic rain drops driving a periodic ripple field. Per-pixel refraction warps the base radial gradient for the rippling-liquid look.": "类似星际之门的事件视界，带有确定性的雨滴驱动周期性的涟漪场。每像素折射会扭曲基底径向渐变，形成波纹般的液体效果。",
