    "The $ symbol — S-curve with a vertical bar through it. Full 3D rotation.": "$符号——带有一条竖线的S形曲线。完整的3D旋转。",
    "The Soviet emblem — a sickle blade crossed by a hammer. Geometry ported from the canonical flag SVG. Full 3D rotation.": "苏联徽章——一把镰刀刀刃，交叉着一把锤子。几何体移植自经典旗帜SVG。完整的3D旋转。",
    "The current map could not be saved.": "当前的地图无法保存。",
