    "The project database could not be loaded. Check the JSON files for parse errors.": "项目数据库无法加载。检查JSON文件是否有解析错误。",
    "The project metadata or map list could not be saved.": "项目元数据或地图列表无法保存。",
    "The taijitu — a disc divided by an S-curve into two interlocking teardrops with opposite-colored dots in each. Full 3D rotation.": "太极图——一个由S形曲线分成两个相互交错的泪滴，每个圆滴中都有相反颜色的点。完整的3D旋转。",
    "The ¥ symbol — Y diagonals + vertical descender + two crossbars. Full 3D rotation.": "¥符号——Y对角线+垂直下降线+两个横杆。完整的3D旋转。",
    "The € symbol — C-arc with two horizontal bars. Full 3D rotation.": "€符号——带两条横杆的C弧。完整的3D旋转。",
    "There are unsaved changes in": "有未保存的更改",
    "There is already an event at this position.": "该位置已经有活动。",
    "Thickness multiplier of each ripple ring.": "每个波纹环的厚度倍增器。",
    "Thickness of the bright disk around the horizon (fraction of event radius). 0 = no disk.": "地平线周围明亮盘的厚度（占事件半径的比例）。0 = 无圆盘。",
    "This command has no parameters.": "该命令没有参数。",
