    "Vertical center of the horizontal arm. 0 = centered (Greek cross); 0.3 = upper third (Latin).": "水平臂的垂直中心。0 = 居中（希腊十字）;0.3 = 上三分之一（拉丁语）。",
    "Vertical center of the shape (fraction of frame height). 0 = top, 0.5 = center, 1 = bottom.": "形状的垂直中心（相框高度的比例）。0 = 上方，0.5 = 中心，1 = 下方。",
    "Vertical cycles each particle completes per loop. Integer for seamless looping.": "垂直循环：每个粒子在每个环路完成。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Vertical extent of the column (column height as a fraction of size). 1.0 = column-as-tall-as-wide, 1.6 = taller transporter pad.": "柱的垂直范围（柱高以尺寸的比例表示）。1.0 = 柱高与宽相同，1.6 = 更高的运输垫。",
