    "Where the rays START (distance from center, fraction of frame). 0 = rays start from the point center.": "射线开始的位置（距离中心，帧的分数）。0 = 射线从点中心开始。",
    "Whip": "鞭子",
    "White-hot center of the beam.": "光束中心白热。",
    "Whole 2D rotations in the screen plane per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每个循环在屏幕平面上做完整的二维旋转。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Whole 2D rotations in the view plane during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "动画过程中视野平面上的整个二维旋转。整数值保持循环无缝。",
    "Whole Map": "全地图",
    "Whole cycles per loop of the underlying noise waves. Integer for seamless looping. Higher = more violent motion.": "每个环路底层噪声波的整个周期。整数用于无缝循环。越高=运动越剧烈。",
    "Whole hue rotations per loop. Integer keeps loop seamless. 0 = static colors.": "每个循环的全色调旋转。整数让循环保持无缝。0 = 静态颜色。",
    "Whole orbits per loop. Integer for seamless looping. 0 = stationary head — use Static Angle to point the tail.": "每圈整圈。整数用于无缝循环。0 = 静止头部 — 使用静态角度指向尾部。",
    "Whole rainbow cycles per loop (hue rotation over time). Integer for seamless looping. 0 = static palette.": "每个循环（色相随时间旋转）的整个彩虹周期。整数用于无缝循环。0 = 静态调色板。",
    "Whole rotations around the X axis per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每个环绕X轴旋转整圈。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Whole rotations around the Y axis per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每个环绕Y轴旋转整圈。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Whole rotations around the vertical axis during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow apparent rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "动画过程中绕垂直轴旋转整圈。整数值保持循环无缝。为了减缓表面旋转，提高顶部的帧数。",
    "Whole rotations around the vertical axis during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "动画过程中绕垂直轴旋转整圈。整数值保持循环无缝。要减缓旋转速度，可以提高顶部的帧数。",
    "Whole rotations forward/back during the animation. Integer values keep the loop seamless. To slow apparent rotation, raise the Frames count at the top.": "动画中整轮前后旋转。整数值保持循环无缝。为了减缓表面旋转，提高顶部的帧数。",
    "Whole rotations of the kaleidoscope pattern per loop. Integer for seamless looping. Positive = clockwise, negative = counter-clockwise, 0 = no rotation.": "每圈万花筒图案的整圈旋转。整数用于无缝循环。正 = 顺时针，负 = 逆时针，0 = 无旋转。",
    "Whole rotations of the ring vertices around the column axis per loop. Integer keeps the loop seamless.": "环顶点绕列轴的整个旋转。整数让循环保持无缝。",
    "Whole rotations of the wisps around the ring per loop. Integer for seamless loop.": "每个环绕环的光丝旋转一整圈。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Whole rotations per loop. Positive = clockwise illusion (inward draw); negative = counter-clockwise (outward push). Integer for seamless loop.": "每圈旋转数。正向 = 顺时针错觉（向内抽）;负 = 逆时针方向（向外推）。整数用于无缝循环。",
    "Whole shimmer-wave cycles per loop along the tail. Integer = seamless loop. 0 = wisps hold a fixed shape; higher = more flowing/rippling motion.": "沿着尾巴，每个环路都有完整的闪烁波周期。整数=无缝循环。0 = 丝状固定;higher = 流动/波纹运动更多。",
    "Whoosh slash through air.": "呼啸，划过空气。",
    "Width at the source (cone base).": "源头（锥体基底）的宽度。",
