    "0 = all drops land at the centre (clean concentric rings expanding outward). 1 = drops scattered across the full disc (chaotic raindrop pattern). Changing this recomputes the simulation.": "0 = semua tetesan mendarat di tengah (cincin konsentris bersih mengembang ke luar). 1 = tetesan yang tersebar di seluruh cakram (pola tetesan hujan yang kacau). Mengubah ini menghitung ulang simulasi.",
    "0 = parallel cylinder beam; 1 = wide cone (tip is 3× source width).": "0 = balok silinder paralel; 1 = kerucut lebar (ujung adalah 3× lebar sumber).",
    "0 = ring layout (nodes on a circle), 1 = grid layout (rectangular mesh).": "0 = tata letak cincin (node pada lingkaran), 1 = tata letak kisi (mesh persegi panjang).",
    "0 = sine-loop (fills then drains seamlessly); 1 = monotonic (0→100% then snaps back at the loop boundary).": "0 = sinus-loop (mengisi lalu mengalirkan dengan mulus); 1 = monoton (0→100% kemudian kembali ke batas loop).",
    "1 = show 45°/135° diagonal cross lines; 0 = cardinal-only.": "1 = menunjukkan garis silang diagonal 45°/135°; 0 = kardinal saja.",
    "1 Step Backward": "1 Melangkah mundur",
    "10 - Maximum": "10 - Maksimum",
    "12-faced regular polyhedron (20 vertices, 30 edges). Golden-ratio geometry.": "Polihedron reguler 12 muka (20 simpul, 30 tepi). Geometri rasio emas.",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer for seamless loop.": "Rotasi 2D di bidang tampilan (seluruh rotasi per loop). Bilangan bulat untuk perulangan mulus.",
    "2D rotation in the view plane (whole rotations per loop). Integer values keep the loop seamless.": "Rotasi 2D di bidang tampilan (seluruh rotasi per loop). Nilai bilangan bulat menjaga loop tetap mulus.",
