    "Text:": "Teks:",
    "The $ symbol — S-curve with a vertical bar through it. Full 3D rotation.": "Simbol $ — kurva-S dengan bilah vertikal melaluinya. Rotasi 3D penuh.",
    "The Soviet emblem — a sickle blade crossed by a hammer. Geometry ported from the canonical flag SVG. Full 3D rotation.": "Lambang Soviet - bilah sabit yang disilangkan oleh palu. Geometri di-porting dari bendera kanonik SVG. Rotasi 3D penuh.",
    "The current map could not be saved.": "Peta saat ini tidak dapat disimpan.",
    "The map could not be saved.": "Peta tidak dapat disimpan.",
    "The map could not be saved. The current view will remain open.": "Peta tidak dapat disimpan. Tampilan saat ini akan tetap terbuka.",
    "The map list could not be saved.": "Daftar peta tidak dapat disimpan.",
    "The new map file could not be saved.": "File peta baru tidak dapat disimpan.",
    "The previous RPG Maker runtime was archived to": "Runtime RPG Maker sebelumnya diarsipkan ke",
    "The project database could not be loaded. Check the JSON files for parse errors.": "Database proyek tidak dapat dimuat. Periksa file JSON untuk kesalahan penguraian.",
    "The project metadata or map list could not be saved.": "Metadata proyek atau daftar peta tidak dapat disimpan.",
    "The taijitu — a disc divided by an S-curve into two interlocking teardrops with opposite-colored dots in each. Full 3D rotation.": "Taijitu — cakram yang dibagi oleh kurva-S menjadi dua tetesan air mata yang saling terkait dengan titik-titik berwarna berlawanan di masing-masingnya. Rotasi 3D penuh.",
    "The ¥ symbol — Y diagonals + vertical descender + two crossbars. Full 3D rotation.": "Simbol ¥ — Diagonal Y + turunan vertikal + dua palang. Rotasi 3D penuh.",
    "The € symbol — C-arc with two horizontal bars. Full 3D rotation.": "Simbol € — C-arc dengan dua bilah horizontal. Rotasi 3D penuh.",
    "There are unsaved changes in": "Ada perubahan yang belum disimpan di",
    "There is already an event at this position.": "Sudah ada acara di posisi ini.",
    "Thickness multiplier of each ripple ring.": "Pengganda ketebalan setiap cincin riak.",
    "Thickness of the bright disk around the horizon (fraction of event radius). 0 = no disk.": "Ketebalan piringan terang di sekitar cakrawala (pecahan jari-jari peristiwa). 0 = tidak ada disk.",
    "This command has no parameters.": "Perintah ini tidak memiliki parameter.",
    "This entry can be removed and saved.": "Entri ini dapat dihapus dan disimpan.",
    "This is a single-character sheet.": "Ini adalah lembar karakter tunggal.",
    "This moves the RPG Maker corescript, js/libs, and index.html into rpgmaker-runtime-backup.zip in the project folder, then installs the Reactor engine files (reactor_*.js and js/libs) in their place.": "Ini memindahkan corescript RPG Maker, js/libs, dan index.html ke rpgmaker-runtime-backup.zip di folder proyek, lalu menginstal file mesin Reaktor (reactor_*.js dan js/libs) di tempatnya.",
    "This plugin has no configurable parameters.": "Plugin ini tidak memiliki parameter yang dapat dikonfigurasi.",
    "This project is already open in another RPG Reactor instance.": "Proyek ini sudah dibuka di instance RPG Reactor lain.",
    "This removes its": "Ini menghapus",
    "This removes their Map###.json files and MapInfos entries.": "Ini menghapus file Map###.json dan entri MapInfos mereka.",
    "This updates the engine files (reactor_*.js and js/libs) to this editor's versions. Your plugin manifest and game data are untouched.": "Ini memperbarui file mesin (reactor_*.js dan js/libs) ke versi editor ini. Manifes plugin dan data game Anda tidak tersentuh.",
